article.headline: Davis, Tezeno propel Southern to 72-63 victory over Jackson State
article.description: — Brandon Davis scored 16 points, Derrick Tezeno had a double-double and Southern beat Jackson State 72-63 on Monday.
article.linkText: Davis, Tezeno propel Southern to 72-63 victory over Jackson State

article.story: JACKSON, Miss. -- — Brandon Davis scored 16 points, Derrick Tezeno had a double-double and Southern beat Jackson State 72-63 on Monday. Davis added seven rebounds for the Jaguars (13-9, 7-2 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Tezeno finished with 15 points and 11 rebounds. Antoine Jacks scored nine with three steals. Ken Evans finished with 16 points to pace the Tigers (8-14, 4-5). Keiveon Hunt added 11 points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
